FILE PREMISSION : 

rwx = read,write,exe

u --> yourself (current user)
g --> group in which user belongs to 
o --> others
a --> all 

ls -ltr 

d rwx rwx rwx
^  ^   ^   ^ other
|  |   |
|  |   | 
|  |   group
|  |
|  rwx for owner form here would be in three parts basically showing does it have the permissions, 
|   if it doesnt then there would be - 
type of file (this case directory)


adding : 	chmod u+r filename (adding read permissin)
removing:	chmod u-r filename (removing)

chmod ugo+r filename
